install mingw
install libxml2
set all needed Environment Variables

Compile it with
gcc adjujda.c level/leveling.c level/level-xml.c level/level-compute.c base/base.c -o adjujda -std=gnu99 -lm -lxml2 -IC:/Glade3/include/libxml2 -static

please replace C:/Glade3/include/libxml2 with your libxml2 header file path.
